<br>
I don't know if you can &quot;do&quot; anything different to keep FV from becoming something other than a roleplay server. I am not saying that to be negative, but I think the only thing the roleplayers can do to keep FV from becoming just another regular server is this...<br>
<br>
Keep on role playing.<br>
<br>
The power gamers will keep on power gaming. Nothing will change that. The role players should just keep on roleplaying and let nothing stop them from doing that either. Persistance will be the key to the role players success on FV.<br>
